[{"text": "108年第一次專門職業及技術人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段", "conf": 0.9995379447937012, "xmin": 39.0, "xmax": 1911.0, "ymin": 37.0, "ymax": 191.0, "cx": 975.0, "cy": 114.25}, {"text": "代號：5106", "conf": 0.9941549301147461, "xmin": 2040.0, "xmax": 2325.0, "ymin": 73.0, "ymax": 151.0, "cx": 2182.5, "cy": 112.0}, {"text": "考試營養師、心理師護理師社會工作師考試試題", "conf": 0.9741684198379517, "xmin": 39.0, "xmax": 1908.0, "ymin": 122.0, "ymax": 274.0, "cx": 973.5, "cy": 197.75}, {"text": "頁次：8-1", "conf": 0.9879817962646484, "xmin": 2047.0, "xmax": 2305.0, "ymin": 133.0, "ymax": 213.0, "cx": 2176.0, "cy": 172.75}, {"text": "等類科", "conf": 0.9761993288993835, "xmin": 38.0, "xmax": 130.0, "ymin": 231.0, "ymax": 490.0, "cx": 84.0, "cy": 360.5}, {"text": "別：高等考試", "conf": 0.9973403811454773, "xmin": 257.0, "xmax": 658.0, "ymin": 250.0, "ymax": 343.0, "cx": 457.5, "cy": 296.5}, {"text": "科：護理師", "conf": 0.9985416531562805, "xmin": 258.0, "xmax": 591.0, "ymin": 333.0, "ymax": 421.0, "cx": 424.5, "cy": 377.25}, {"text": "目：精神科與社區衛生護理學", "conf": 0.9997392296791077, "xmin": 267.0, "xmax": 1090.0, "ymin": 418.0, "ymax": 516.0, "cx": 678.5, "cy": 467.0}, {"text": "考試時間：1小時", "conf": 0.9498641490936279, "xmin": 43.0, "xmax": 597.0, "ymin": 485.0, "ymax": 589.0, "cx": 320.25, "cy": 537.0}, {"text": "座號：", "conf": 0.9830524325370789, "xmin": 1687.0, "xmax": 1867.0, "ymin": 537.0, "ymax": 609.0, "cx": 1777.0, "cy": 572.75}, {"text": "注意：(一)本試題為單一選擇題，請選出一個正確或最適當的答案，複選作答者，該題不予計分。", "conf": 0.9338987469673157, "xmin": 44.0, "xmax": 2051.0, "ymin": 596.0, "ymax": 713.0, "cx": 1047.75, "cy": 654.5}, {"text": "(二)本科目共80題，每題125分，須用2B鉛筆在試卡上依題號清楚劃記，於本試題上作答者，不予計分。", "conf": 0.9360698461532593, "xmin": 250.0, "xmax": 2330.0, "ymin": 671.0, "ymax": 771.0, "cx": 1290.0, "cy": 721.25}, {"text": "(三)禁止使用電子計算器。", "conf": 0.9435867071151733, "xmin": 258.0, "xmax": 772.0, "ymin": 743.0, "ymax": 817.0, "cx": 515.0, "cy": 780.25}, {"text": "1", "conf": 0.999257504940033, "xmin": 86.0, "xmax": 118.0, "ymin": 857.0, "ymax": 908.0, "cx": 102.0, "cy": 882.5}, {"text": "世界衛生組織強調對精神病人基本人權的尊重，下列何者正確？", "conf": 0.9928128123283386, "xmin": 182.0, "xmax": 1558.0, "ymin": 855.0, "ymax": 945.0, "cx": 870.25, "cy": 900.0}, {"text": "(A)病人應有權利在社區，而非機構化照顧", "conf": 0.9942228198051453, "xmin": 187.0, "xmax": 1083.0, "ymin": 938.0, "ymax": 1019.0, "cx": 635.25, "cy": 978.5}, {"text": "(B)全球心理衛生治療的趨勢是從急性醫院轉換為慢性機構療養", "conf": 0.9990130662918091, "xmin": 190.0, "xmax": 1522.0, "ymin": 1022.0, "ymax": 1101.0, "cx": 856.0, "cy": 1061.5}, {"text": "(C)精神生物醫學的進步，藥物治療的成效佳，故不需要心理社會的整合性照護", "conf": 0.9971012473106384, "xmin": 192.0, "xmax": 1863.0, "ymin": 1104.0, "ymax": 1185.0, "cx": 1027.25, "cy": 1144.25}, {"text": "(D)慢性精神病人宜在偏遠地區的療養機構接受治療與安置", "conf": 0.9964872002601624, "xmin": 193.0, "xmax": 1429.0, "ymin": 1185.0, "ymax": 1261.0, "cx": 810.75, "cy": 1223.0}, {"text": "2", "conf": 0.999921441078186, "xmin": 92.0, "xmax": 133.0, "ymin": 1267.0, "ymax": 1320.0, "cx": 112.5, "cy": 1293.5}, {"text": "關於心理防衛機轉（defense mechanism），「把自己無法接受的想法與情緒，推給其他人，認為是", "conf": 0.9840456247329712, "xmin": 188.0, "xmax": 2333.0, "ymin": 1261.0, "ymax": 1350.0, "cx": 1260.5, "cy": 1305.5}, {"text": "別人擁有這樣的想法，而不是他自己。", "conf": 0.9657912254333496, "xmin": 192.0, "xmax": 1011.0, "ymin": 1348.0, "ymax": 1421.0, "cx": 601.25, "cy": 1384.5}, {"text": "指的是下列何種心理防衛機轉？", "conf": 0.986871063709259, "xmin": 1075.0, "xmax": 1753.0, "ymin": 1364.0, "ymax": 1421.0, "cx": 1413.75, "cy": 1392.5}, {"text": "C", "conf": 0.45984408259391785, "xmin": 1000.0, "xmax": 1019.0, "ymin": 1377.0, "ymax": 1395.0, "cx": 1009.5, "cy": 1386.0}, {"text": "」", "conf": 0.9996505975723267, "xmin": 1037.0, "xmax": 1099.0, "ymin": 1374.0, "ymax": 1414.0, "cx": 1068.25, "cy": 1394.0}, {"text": "(A)合理化（rationalization）", "conf": 0.9324985146522522, "xmin": 196.0, "xmax": 762.0, "ymin": 1429.0, "ymax": 1498.0, "cx": 479.0, "cy": 1463.5}, {"text": "(B)壓抑（suppression）", "conf": 0.9274542927742004, "xmin": 1249.0, "xmax": 1702.0, "ymin": 1440.0, "ymax": 1505.0, "cx": 1475.5, "cy": 1472.5}, {"text": "(C)反向行為（reaction formation）", "conf": 0.9217161536216736, "xmin": 198.0, "xmax": 892.0, "ymin": 1513.0, "ymax": 1578.0, "cx": 545.0, "cy": 1545.75}, {"text": "(D)投射（projection）", "conf": 0.9228979349136353, "xmin": 1251.0, "xmax": 1674.0, "ymin": 1524.0, "ymax": 1581.0, "cx": 1462.5, "cy": 1552.75}, {"text": "3", "conf": 0.9999022483825684, "xmin": 96.0, "xmax": 133.0, "ymin": 1594.0, "ymax": 1644.0, "cx": 114.5, "cy": 1619.0}, {"text": "服役的林先生對軍中訓練的要求一直無法達成，常出現失眠、肚子痛等現象。某日要出外打靶的早", "conf": 0.9926035404205322, "xmin": 191.0, "xmax": 2332.0, "ymin": 1590.0, "ymax": 1667.0, "cx": 1261.5, "cy": 1628.5}, {"text": "上，林先生突然雙腳麻痺無法站立，緊急送醫並無發現任何異常的病理報告，因此轉介精神科治療，", "conf": 0.9979598522186279, "xmin": 196.0, "xmax": 2323.0, "ymin": 1676.0, "ymax": 1740.0, "cx": 1259.5, "cy": 1708.0}, {"text": "下列何者為林先生使用的心理防衛機轉?", "conf": 0.9740743637084961, "xmin": 197.0, "xmax": 1075.0, "ymin": 1757.0, "ymax": 1816.0, "cx": 636.0, "cy": 1786.5}, {"text": "(A)退化", "conf": 0.9760336875915527, "xmin": 190.0, "xmax": 355.0, "ymin": 1833.0, "ymax": 1907.0, "cx": 272.5, "cy": 1869.75}, {"text": "(B)轉化", "conf": 0.953728973865509, "xmin": 709.0, "xmax": 872.0, "ymin": 1835.0, "ymax": 1899.0, "cx": 790.5, "cy": 1867.0}, {"text": "(C）否定", "conf": 0.8523423075675964, "xmin": 1252.0, "xmax": 1408.0, "ymin": 1840.0, "ymax": 1897.0, "cx": 1330.0, "cy": 1868.5}, {"text": "(D)昇華", "conf": 0.8894468545913696, "xmin": 1781.0, "xmax": 1937.0, "ymin": 1839.0, "ymax": 1896.0, "cx": 1859.0, "cy": 1867.5}, {"text": "4", "conf": 0.999752938747406, "xmin": 97.0, "xmax": 135.0, "ymin": 1919.0, "ymax": 1967.0, "cx": 116.0, "cy": 1943.0}, {"text": "有關佩普洛（Peplau）概念的敘述，下列何者正確？①護病關係的介紹期、認同期、工作期及結束期，", "conf": 0.969416618347168, "xmin": 192.0, "xmax": 2324.0, "ymin": 1916.0, "ymax": 1982.0, "cx": 1258.0, "cy": 1949.0}, {"text": "是重疊及連接的僱②強調護理人員使用治療性人際溝通技巧和病人建立關係", "conf": 0.9770099520683289, "xmin": 193.0, "xmax": 1839.0, "ymin": 1994.0, "ymax": 2059.0, "cx": 1016.0, "cy": 2026.5}, {"text": "③協助病人將現在的", "conf": 0.9988090991973877, "xmin": 1878.0, "xmax": 2326.0, "ymin": 1999.0, "ymax": 2054.0, "cx": 2102.0, "cy": 2026.5}, {"text": "經驗與其他經驗統合", "conf": 0.9993063807487488, "xmin": 196.0, "xmax": 642.0, "ymin": 2082.0, "ymax": 2133.0, "cx": 419.0, "cy": 2107.5}, {"text": "④透過轉移關係來幫助病人了解自己", "conf": 0.9904211163520813, "xmin": 694.0, "xmax": 1478.0, "ymin": 2077.0, "ymax": 2130.0, "cx": 1086.0, "cy": 2103.5}, {"text": "(A)①②③", "conf": 0.9839935302734375, "xmin": 192.0, "xmax": 398.0, "ymin": 2156.0, "ymax": 2221.0, "cx": 294.75, "cy": 2188.5}, {"text": "(B)②③④", "conf": 0.9309297204017639, "xmin": 716.0, "xmax": 915.0, "ymin": 2157.0, "ymax": 2210.0, "cx": 815.5, "cy": 2183.5}, {"text": "(C)①③④", "conf": 0.9582955241203308, "xmin": 1254.0, "xmax": 1455.0, "ymin": 2160.0, "ymax": 2213.0, "cx": 1354.5, "cy": 2186.5}, {"text": "(D)①②④", "conf": 0.9516575336456299, "xmin": 1786.0, "xmax": 1987.0, "ymin": 2157.0, "ymax": 2210.0, "cx": 1886.5, "cy": 2183.5}, {"text": "5", "conf": 0.9997422099113464, "xmin": 94.0, "xmax": 132.0, "ymin": 2243.0, "ymax": 2293.0, "cx": 113.0, "cy": 2268.0}, {"text": "李小姐已住院一個月和護理師會談提到：「一直以來只相信自己，也獨力把自己照顧得很好。」護", "conf": 0.9976091384887695, "xmin": 193.0, "xmax": 2327.0, "ymin": 2233.0, "ymax": 2298.0, "cx": 1260.0, "cy": 2265.25}, {"text": "理師回應表示：「你認為自己把自己照顧得很好，最近半年出現多次割腕的狀況是發生什麼狀況？」", "conf": 0.9965139031410217, "xmin": 191.0, "xmax": 2333.0, "ymin": 2311.0, "ymax": 2378.0, "cx": 1262.0, "cy": 2344.5}, {"text": "此回應是屬於何種治療性溝通技巧?", "conf": 0.9819591045379639, "xmin": 194.0, "xmax": 975.0, "ymin": 2398.0, "ymax": 2456.0, "cx": 584.5, "cy": 2427.0}, {"text": "(A)提出懷疑（voicing doubt）", "conf": 0.9275819659233093, "xmin": 197.0, "xmax": 796.0, "ymin": 2482.0, "ymax": 2539.0, "cx": 496.5, "cy": 2510.5}, {"text": "(B)鼓勵比較（encouragingcomparison）", "conf": 0.9661113023757935, "xmin": 1256.0, "xmax": 2062.0, "ymin": 2478.0, "ymax": 2528.0, "cx": 1659.0, "cy": 2503.0}, {"text": "(C）面質（confrontation）", "conf": 0.9559881091117859, "xmin": 195.0, "xmax": 691.0, "ymin": 2561.0, "ymax": 2617.0, "cx": 442.75, "cy": 2589.25}, {"text": "(D)鼓勵評價（encouraging evaluation）", "conf": 0.9531840682029724, "xmin": 1254.0, "xmax": 2038.0, "ymin": 2556.0, "ymax": 2607.0, "cx": 1646.0, "cy": 2581.75}, {"text": "6", "conf": 0.9998160004615784, "xmin": 93.0, "xmax": 134.0, "ymin": 2643.0, "ymax": 2696.0, "cx": 113.5, "cy": 2669.5}, {"text": "「一朝被蛇咬，十年怕草繩」此例子可以運用下列何種理論說明焦慮反應的產生？", "conf": 0.9942887425422668, "xmin": 212.0, "xmax": 1959.0, "ymin": 2632.0, "ymax": 2699.0, "cx": 1085.5, "cy": 2665.5}, {"text": "(B)學習", "conf": 0.9707881212234497, "xmin": 709.0, "xmax": 869.0, "ymin": 2716.0, "ymax": 2781.0, "cx": 789.0, "cy": 2748.5}, {"text": "(C)認知", "conf": 0.9339761734008789, "xmin": 1248.0, "xmax": 1405.0, "ymin": 2713.0, "ymax": 2771.0, "cx": 1326.5, "cy": 2742.0}, {"text": "(D）人際", "conf": 0.8251897692680359, "xmin": 1781.0, "xmax": 1940.0, "ymin": 2711.0, "ymax": 2774.0, "cx": 1860.5, "cy": 2742.25}, {"text": "(A)心理分析", "conf": 0.992145836353302, "xmin": 193.0, "xmax": 441.0, "ymin": 2726.0, "ymax": 2781.0, "cx": 317.0, "cy": 2753.5}, {"text": "7", "conf": 0.9997624754905701, "xmin": 90.0, "xmax": 131.0, "ymin": 2805.0, "ymax": 2856.0, "cx": 110.5, "cy": 2830.5}, {"text": "何先生因準備進行電氣痙攣療法（electroconvulsive therapy,ECT）而顯焦慮，護理師和其討論並提供", "conf": 0.9867486357688904, "xmin": 192.0, "xmax": 2328.0, "ymin": 2795.0, "ymax": 2860.0, "cx": 1260.0, "cy": 2827.5}, {"text": "②治療前要先拿下活動假牙", "conf": 0.9996070861816406, "xmin": 1568.0, "xmax": 2184.0, "ymin": 2880.0, "ymax": 2930.0, "cx": 1876.0, "cy": 2905.0}, {"text": "③治", "conf": 0.9994129538536072, "xmin": 2227.0, "xmax": 2331.0, "ymin": 2874.0, "ymax": 2932.0, "cx": 2279.0, "cy": 2903.0}, {"text": "相關護理指導，下列何者正確？①治療後有暫時的記憶力喪失", "conf": 0.9995447993278503, "xmin": 192.0, "xmax": 1545.0, "ymin": 2877.0, "ymax": 2943.0, "cx": 868.5, "cy": 2910.0}, {"text": "療前會給予註射 Demerol 藥物", "conf": 0.9619864225387573, "xmin": 193.0, "xmax": 844.0, "ymin": 2966.0, "ymax": 3022.0, "cx": 518.25, "cy": 2994.0},